AndTricks":["You can use tinned passionfruit pulp if fresh ones are not in season. We recommend straining passionfruit to remove seeds.","You can store truffles in sealed container in the refrigerator for up to 1 week."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","3h 30m","30 portions"]}